data.description: Discover the perfect blend of style and functionality in this 4-bed, 3-bath split-level home. Designed with a great floor plan, this residence offers an ideal layout for comfortable living. The separate master wing creates a private retreat, featuring a spacious bedroom, very large walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom.  Entertain effortlessly in the open-concept living area, flooded with natural light from large windows. The kitchen, adorned with modern finishes, seamlessly connects to the dining space.  Three additional bedrooms provide versatility for guests or a home office. With a thoughtful split-level design, this home offers distinct living zones, perfect for various activities. Modern fixtures, ample storage, and a two-car garage complete the package.  Conveniently located and meticulously designed, this home is a must-see. Schedule your viewing now and seize the opportunity to call this split-level gem your own!
